= SDL_iconv_string =

This function converts a string between encodings in one pass, returning a string that must be freed with [[SDL_free]]() or NULL on error.

== Syntax ==

<syntaxhighlight lang='c'>
char* SDL_iconv_string(const char *tocode,
                       const char *fromcode,
                       const char *inbuf,
                       size_t inbytesleft);
</syntaxhighlight>

